= SDL_GetAudioStatus =
Use this function to get the current audio state.


== Syntax ==
```c++
SDL_audiostatus SDL_GetAudioStatus(void)
```

== Return Value ==
Returns the current audio state:
:SDL_AUDIO_STOPPED
:SDL_AUDIO_PLAYING
:SDL_AUDIO_PAUSED

